, 26, pp. 3469-3472; Steele, M., Morley, R., Ermold, W., PHC: Global ocean hydrography with a high-quality Arctic Ocean (2001) J. Climate, 14, pp. 2079-2087; Stevens, D.P., The open boundary condition in the United Kingdom fine-resolution antarctic model (1991) J. Phys. Oceanogr., 21, pp. 1494-1499; Tremblay, L.-B., Can we consider the Arctic oscillation independently from the Barents Oscillation? (2001) Geophys. Res. Lett., 28, pp. 4227-4230; Tucker, W.B., Weatherly, J.M., Eppler, D.T., Farmer, L.D., Evidence for rapid thinning of sea ice in the western Arctic Ocean at the end of the 1980s (2001) Geophys. Res. Lett., 28, pp. 2851-2854; Vinje, T., Fram strait ice fluxes and atmospheric circulation: 1950-2000 (2001) J. Climate, 14, pp. 3508-3517; Vinje, T., Nordlund, N., Kvambek, A., Monitoring ice thickness in Fram Strait (1998) J. Geophys. Res., 103, pp. 10437-10449; Wadhams, P., Evidence for thinning of the Arctic ice cover north of Greenland (1990) Nature, 345, pp. 795-797; Wadhams, P., Davis, N.R., Further evidence of ice thinning in the Arctic Ocean (2000) Geophys. Res. Lett., 27, pp. 3973-3975; Winsor, P., Arctic sea ice thickness remained constant during the 1990's (2001) Geophys. Res. Lett., 28, pp. 1039-1041; Zalesak, S.T., Fully multidimensional flux-corrected transport algorithms for fluids (1979) J. Comput. Phys., 31, pp. 335-362; Zhang, J., Rothrock, D., Steele, M., Recent changes in Arctic sea ice: The interplay between ice dynamics and thermodynamics (2000) J. Climate, 13, pp. 3099-3114","Gerdes, R.; Alfred-Wegener-Inst. Polar/Meeresfo., Bussestr. 24, Bremerhaven D-27570, Germany; email: rgerdes@awi-bremerhaven.de",,,,,,,,08948755,,,,"English","J. Clim.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-0141571609
